The flapping about ! Me sitting doing nothing and him on the go like a rocket . 
But he wants you , George he wants you . 
Says he can make a splash but can't keep on . 
Says if you don't come in everything will smash But you are coming in ? She paused and looked at me . 
Well You don't say you won't come in ! But look here , aunt , I said , do you understand quite ? . 
There's no law against selling quack medicine that I know of , said my aunt . 
She thought for a minute and became unusually grave . 
It's our only chance , George , she said . 
