Lads and lasses dancing on the village green . 
Yule Log all the rest of it . 
How would old Sally Glue do for a May Queen ? asked one of the sons in the slight pause that followed . 
Or Annie Glassbound ? said the other , with the huge virile guffaw of a young man whose voice has only recently broken . 
Sally Glue is eighty five , explained the vicar , and Annie Glassbound is well a young lady of extremely generous proportions . 
And not quite right , you know . 
Generous proportions ! said the eldest son , and the guffaws were renewed . 
You see , said the vicar , all the brisker girls go into service in or near London . 
The life of excitement attracts them . 
And no doubt the higher wages have something to do with it . 
And the liberty to wear finery . 
And generally freedom from restraint . 
